Package: rpkgdev
Title: R Package Development Workflow Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Blas", "Benito", , "blasbenito@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Comprehensive suite of development workflow functions for R package
    development. Provides dev_*() functions for common tasks like testing,
    checking, building documentation, and CRAN release preparation. Includes
    deploy_template() to scaffold new packages with complete development
    infrastructure.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/blasbenito/rpkgdev
BugReports: https://github.com/blasbenito/rpkgdev/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
